message:
Hey Everyone!

We are trying to organize a trip to go to the TOGETHER event (http://reset2016.com/) in Washington D.C. this July 16th and we need YOUR help. I am asking everyone to fill out this survey ASAP and then share it with other people you know who would be interested or other Christians you know on campus. Please fill this survey out before this Friday, May 20th.

http://z.umn.edu/together16
